    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "sn47.30:1.1",
          "pli": "Taṃyeva nidānaṃ. ",
          "en": "The same setting. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn47.30:1.2",
          "pli": "Tena kho pana samayena mānadinno gahapati ābādhiko hoti dukkhito bāḷhagilāno. ",
          "en": "Now at that time the householder Mānadinna was sick, suffering, gravely ill. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn47.30:1.3",
          "pli": "Atha kho mānadinno gahapati aññataraṃ purisaṃ āmantesi: ",
          "en": "Then he addressed a man: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn47.30:1.4",
          "pli": "“ehi tvaṃ, ambho purisa … pe … ",
          "en": "“Please, mister, go to Venerable Ānanda …” … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn47.30:1.5",
          "pli": "na me, bhante, khamanīyaṃ na yāpanīyaṃ. Bāḷhā me dukkhā vedanā abhikkamanti, no paṭikkamanti; abhikkamosānaṃ paññāyati, no paṭikkamoti. ",
          "en": "“Sir, I’m not keeping well, I’m not alright. The pain is terrible and growing, not fading; its growing is evident, not its fading. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn47.30:1.6",
          "pli": "Evarūpāya cāhaṃ, bhante, dukkhāya vedanāya phuṭṭho samāno kāye kāyānupassī viharāmi ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ; ",
          "en": "When I experience such painful feelings I meditate observing an aspect of the body—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn47.30:1.7",
          "pli": "vedanāsu … pe … ",
          "en": "I meditate observing an aspect of feelings … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn47.30:1.8",
          "pli": "citte … pe … ",
          "en": "mind … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn47.30:1.9",
          "pli": "dhammesu dhammānupassī viharāmi ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ. ",
          "en": "principles—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn47.30:1.10",
          "pli": "Yāni cimāni, bhante, bhagavatā pañcorambhāgiyāni saṃyojanāni desitāni, nāhaṃ, bhante, tesaṃ kiñci attani appahīnaṃ samanupassāmī”ti. ",
          "en": "And of the five lower fetters taught by the Buddha, I don’t see any that I haven’t given up.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn47.30:1.11",
          "pli": "“Lābhā te, gahapati, suladdhaṃ te, gahapati. ",
          "en": "“You’re fortunate, householder, so very fortunate! "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn47.30:1.12",
          "pli": "Anāgāmiphalaṃ tayā, gahapati, byākatan”ti. ",
          "en": "You have declared the fruit of non-return.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn47.30:1.13",
          "pli": "Dasamaṃ. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn47.30:1.14",
          "pli": "Sīlaṭṭhitivaggo tatiyo. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn47.30:2.1",
          "pli": "Sīlaṃ ṭhiti parihānaṃ, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn47.30:2.2",
          "pli": "suddhaṃ brāhmaṇapadesaṃ; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn47.30:2.3",
          "pli": "Samattaṃ loko sirivaḍḍho, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn47.30:2.4",
          "pli": "mānadinnena te dasāti. ",
          "en": ""
        }
      ],
